@startuml High School Story — Daily Loop

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor #EBF8FF
    BorderColor #2B6CB0
    FontSize 11
}
skinparam activityDiamond {
    BackgroundColor #FFF5F5
    BorderColor #C53030
}
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FFFBEB
    BorderColor #D69E2E
    FontSize 10
}

title A Typical School Day (Monday–Friday)

start

:☀️ **06:00** — Wake Up;
note right : Energy restores from sleep\nStress partially clears

:🧹 Morning Routine (dorm room);
note right : Manage inventory / backpack\nCheck phone (messages, schedule)\nOptional: quick study session

:🚶 **06:45** — Travel to School;
note right : Walk from dorm\nNo time cost (adjacent)

:📋 **07:00** — Homeroom;
note right : Attendance, announcements\nPassive NPC interaction opportunity

repeat
    :📚 **Class Period** (45 min);
    note right : Enter Classroom Mechanic\n→ see classroom.puml

    :🚶 **Break** (15 min);
    note right : Move to any school zone\nQuick NPC interaction\nUse items (consumables)
repeat while (more classes before lunch?) is (yes)

:🍽️ **12:00–13:00** — Lunch Break;
note right : Visit cafeteria, lounge, library\nSocialize with NPCs (Rel. gain)\nEat (Energy +, Stress –)\nPhone use OK

repeat
    :📚 **Afternoon Class Period** (45 min);
    note right : Same classroom mechanic

    :🚶 **Break** (15 min);
repeat while (more afternoon classes?) is (yes)

:🔔 **~14:45** — School Day Ends;

fork
    :🎭 **Club Hour** (if club day);
    note right : Mon / Wed / Fri\nClub activity → stat gains\nNPC relationship opportunities
fork again
    :🏃 **After-School Free Time**;
    note right : Visit town locations\nPart-time job (if signed up)\nHangout with NPC
end fork

:🌆 **Afternoon / Evening Free Time**;
note right : Multiple time slots available\nEach action costs 15–60 min

:🏠 **Return to Dorm by 22:00**;
note right : Curfew enforced\nLate return: Stress +, potential penalty

:🌙 **Dorm Evening** (22:00–23:00);
note right : Study / read / phone\nReceive NPC calls or visits\nJournal / reflect

:💤 **23:00 — Sleep** (enforced);
note right : Energy restores based on sleep time\nStress partially clears\nSome NPC arcs trigger on certain nights

stop

note as N1
    **Special days:**
    Saturday/Sunday — no school.
    Full day of free time + Farmers Market (Saturday).
    Weekend jobs available.
    NPC schedules shift on weekends.
end note

@enduml
